# This is the umbrella/coordination repo for the coarsening-at-random paper
# family. Each paper and the simulation backend is its OWN independent git
# repository with its own remote and Zenodo DOI; they are deliberately NOT
# tracked here (no submodules). This repo holds only the shared coordination
# files. The README publication tracker links to each paper's own repo.

# Independent paper repos (own .git, remote, Zenodo DOI; two are symlinks
# into ~/github/masked/).
papers/

# Independent simulation repo (github.com/queelius/scrna-coarsening-sims).
sims/

# Internal strategy notes, not for the public landing page.
.ecosystem/

# Operational Zenodo support-request drafts (kept local).
.zenodo_support_request_*.md

# Secrets and tooling state that must never be committed. The Zenodo API
# token lives in ~/.zenodo.toml (outside this tree); guard against any stray
# TOML being added here.
.zenodo.toml
*.toml
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~
